g.title: j3063291926
g.text: So. How many of you are there?

g.title: j2465853024
g.text: Why're you asking?

g.title: j3333755517
g.text: None of your business. [End.]

g.title: j3828802090
g.text: Just me and the kid that I know of.

g.title: j195082406

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.title: j2736379545
g.text: That you know of?

g.title: j4163611935
g.text: You've been inside my head. I guess I'm curious to know more about what's going on inside yours.

g.title: j107163864
g.text: At the rate my life is going? Duplicates would be pretty mundane, honestly.

g.title: j460639737
g.text: Who knows how many more universes there could be out there?

g.title: j4010130203
g.text: Technically, I'm not in your head.

g.title: j1534872472
g.text: You sure? It can get strange in here.

g.title: j851246635
g.text: Picture it. Drifters, as far as the eye can see...

g.title: j948092838
g.text: More versions of you? Me? Us?

g.title: j2062819004
g.text: I'm just driving your body.

g.title: j979832392
g.text: Have you met my sister? You've got nothing on her.

g.title: j4090819077
g.text: Maybe I'd finally get my laundry folded.

g.title: j1789703820
g.text: Can you imagine the arguing? And the sass?

g.title: j2725928165
g.text: I don't know, I think it'd be pretty awesome.

g.title: j2569147754
g.text: Poor sods.

g.title: j3330015903
g.text: Nope. Still weird, and I still hate it when you say it.

g.title: j2545114792
g.text: Considering what she's been through? I think she has the right to be "strange."

g.title: j4276731744
g.text: We'll see about that.

g.title: j441421596
g.text: Although... more Drifters = more laundry...

g.title: j3770021903
g.text: Absolutely not.

g.title: j3375185816
g.text: Speak for yourself.

g.title: j3290317091
g.text: Maybe there's one where we're dating...

g.title: j2613466982
g.text: If it makes you feel better, I bet there's at least *one* where you won the fight. :P

g.title: j2862616315
g.text: Raise one for all the Alternate Arthurs and Different Drifters.

g.title: j4148726912
g.text: Anyway. Seriously, how many of you *are* there?

g.title: j560195338
g.text: She was only marginally more normal when we were children.

g.title: j2881473279
g.text: Something to look forward to.

g.title: j1042056691
g.text: Damn. Thwarted again!

g.title: j3254595788
g.text: To be fair, I'm not sure I'd want to deal with a room full of Arthurs.

g.title: j3972956922
g.text: I repeat: Poor sods.

g.title: j826694191
g.text: Har, har.

g.title: j3810445272
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j3427491169
g.text: Why, fantasizing about two of me? ;)

g.title: j577845960

g.title: j1562450699
g.text: All of us, glowering at each other in silence. Brooding.

g.title: j2321185606
g.text: I can drink to that.

g.title: j641025407
g.text: Don't flatter yourself.

g.title: j4192074355
g.text: HAH.

g.title: j1693723514
g.text: We'd at least get things done, I suppose.

g.title: j350271754
g.text: Well, let's just hope we don't end up with Infinite Laundry, yeah?
